productions accounted for $10.3 billion in lost revenues and more
than 20,000 jobs. Through the first nine months this year, filming
at locations off studio lots declined 6 percent from the same
period of 1998 in Los Angeles County.
</P>
<P>
   X X X
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
