<HEADLINE>
MORNINGS, THEY LIKE TO WATCH 
</HEADLINE>
  (The Week in Review) 
(NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For international clients' use by
special arrangement only. Asian and European points: contact Karl
Horwitz in Paris for details and prices (Phone: 47 42 17 11; FAX:
47-42-80-44). Latin American points: contact Olivia Vasquez in Los
Angeles (Phone: 310-996-0075; FAX: 310-996-0089) 
(bl) 
 By JAMES BARRON   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK _ East Side, West Side, all around the town,
early-morning television is taking to the sidewalks of New York as
never before _ sidewalks that have become, in effect, sound stages
where cameras can capture the exuberance of nose-to-the-glass fans
waving, shouting and reveling in their 15 seconds of fame.
</P>
