(Phoenix),
</P>
<P>
   _ Back: Darrell Armstrong, Michael Doleac, Matt Harpring,
Charles Outlaw, Derek Strong.
</P>
<P>
   _ Outlook: The Magic ripped its team apart to create maximum cap
room, and they're headed for the lottery, while eating a number of
contracts. Will that strategy attract a Tim Duncan or a Grant Hill?
Stay tuned.
</P>
