(Shaquille O'Neal) and high-scoring guard and forward (Kobe Bryant
and Glen Rice). But can Jackson make the individual talent work as
a team? Jackson had the luxury of coaching Michael Jordan in
Chicago, but this Laker team is much different. (Denberg, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 25. MOVED
