<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-30 19:46 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3592 &Cx1f; ttx-z
r s BC-FBN-COWBOYS-COLTS-TEX     10-30 0558
