<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-30 20:54 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3658 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s BC-FBN-RYAN-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      10-30 1043
